  • Constructor Details

    • ExomiserMvStoreMetadataServiceFactory

      @Deprecated(forRemoval=true, since="2.0.3") public ExomiserMvStoreMetadataServiceFactory(Map<GenomeBuild,Path> exomiserDbPaths)
      Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
      Since Exomiser 14.0.0, the pathogenicity scores, allele frequencies data and clinvar are distributed in separate MV stores. Use fromResources(Map) instead and provide ExomiserResources with paths to variant and clinvar database files for each GenomeBuild. To be removed in 3.0.0.
      Parameters:
      exomiserDbPaths - map with Path to variant database for a GenomeBuild. Usually, this file is called 2309_hg38_variants.mv.db or similar.
